  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="section bg-white" id="what-is">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">What Is Dog Daycare Software?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <strong>Dog daycare software</strong> is a specialized management platform designed specifically for dog daycare facilities. Unlike generic booking systems or spreadsheets, it includes industry-specific features like playgroup management, vaccination tracking, and report cards.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          The best platforms handle reservations, deposits, packages, vaccination records with automatic expiry alerts, capacity management by weight class or temperament, digital report cards with photo sharing, owner messaging, automated reminders, and integrated billing—all from one unified system.
        </p>
