          At PetCare.Software, we built tools specifically for mixed facilities—so if you also run <a href="/dog-boarding-software/" class="text-brand-red hover:underline">dog boarding</a>, a <a href="/kennel-software/" class="text-brand-red hover:underline">kennel</a>, or even a <a href="/cattery-software/" class="text-brand-red hover:underline">cattery</a>, you can manage everything from one login without switching between multiple systems.
        </p>

        <h2 id="features" class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-12 mb-6">Must-Have Features</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Online Bookings & Deposits</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">24/7 reservations with optional deposits to reduce no-shows. Owners book when it's convenient for them, not just during your business hours.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Capacity & Playgroup Rules</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Real-time controls to avoid overbooking—by weight class, temperament, room, or total capacity. Prevents double bookings and unsafe playgroup mixes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Owner Portal</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Clients upload vaccine proofs, sign waivers, update contact/pet info, view report cards, check balances, and pay online without calling you.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Report Cards & Media</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Branded updates with notes, photos, or links to short videos. Owners love seeing their pups throughout the day. Builds loyalty and referrals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Add-ons & Upsells</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Offer enrichment, nail trims, baths, or late pickup fees during checkout. Increases average booking value by 15-25%.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Vaccination Tracking</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Automatic expiry alerts sent 30-60 days before vaccines expire. Block bookings for non-compliant pets until records are updated. 100% compliance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

