          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-brand-red text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">✓</div>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-brand-navy">Increased revenue:</strong>
              <span class="text-gray-700"> Add-ons, packages, and reduced no-shows boost average booking value by 15-25%. Deposits reduce no-shows by 40-60%.</span>
